We have some very sad news from State Senator Bruce McPherson. On Saturday
morning, his 27 year old son was murdered in San Francisco during an
attempted robbery. Hunter McPherson will be remembered during a  memorial
service in Aptos on Wednesday, November 21.

The family has also set up an athletic scholarship fund in his name. We have
additional information if you need it.

Please remember this wonderful family in your thoughts and prayers.

-Lang, Hansen, O'Malley & Miller